3b0f094","tid":1569880,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:59:34.000Z","msg":"深夜推po"},{"pid":"1f7d0a15de472a125123208b23765d856e366961","tid":1569880,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:59:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">721 <br />\n831 <br />\n新屋嶺集中營</span></strong>"},{"pid":"701b2f1012aa96ef8d7d76f27b7ed414a7682763","tid":1569880,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692810afeaf7322a4d304967d722970cfcfe6de6","tid":1569880,"uid":273032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:06:05.000Z","msg":"係呀 我地要諗對策<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:25:57.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n915 維園中秋綵燈會、祈禱會、大合唱<br />\n@黑幫引手足，警察拉手足<br />\n@小心被暴徒跟蹤<br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆戰線受襲！唱歌後連儂，有你有我<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n@Template@<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>（注意安全）；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=dec9ed19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.15 @Template End@"},{"pid":"0fbeb84104f46234cbb576570ad7c5700922239a","tid":1569880,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa9de114b0ad2fb7c556cedbb99a5adc94ffe755","tid":1569880,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:39:26.000Z","msg":"卧底 僆儂牆 打藍蛆 <br />\n全民進化"},{"pid":"b358b243a4ea733030e03b0e40d65ef1cb9f28c6","tid":1569880,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:55:02.000Z","msg":"藍絲廢老冇成本有錢收咪會出黎<br />\n<br />\n但當佢地知道出黎會被人打到仆街<br />\n雙工都唔會再出<br />\n因為佢地唔係黑社會<br />\n命仔緊要過錢"},{"pid":"0662c5f9ac26cfc94a61b3574be74ddc4e2fd7d9","tid":1569880,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93b08f2f8122e0836fe36ab0f4820b3a6135cc68","tid":1569880,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}